node.text: I've got a special guest today, my good friend Janelle Cohen (@straightenupbyjanelle), who is an interior decorator and organizer extraordinaire. She completely changed my life by helping me relieve stress through de-cluttering. Stay tuned to find out her secrets 👗 👠 📦

node.text:
Loving the new @olehenriksen Dewtopia 20% Acid Night Treatment. If you have been following me you know I love this brand, and this product has quickly become a staple in my nighttime routine. This is their most potent acid serum to date, and it’s already making such a difference for any uneven texture.  Excited to keep using it!
Available online at olehenriksen.com and @sephora #dewitbig #olehenriksenpartner
